<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>PDF Fusion - Extended Freelancer Contract Agreement</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'application', media: 'all' %>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row template-container">
            <div class="card p-3">
                <h5 class="text-center">Freelancer Contract Agreement</h5>
                <p>This contract establishes a working relationship between the client and the freelancer for the completion of a specific project or set of tasks.</p>
                

                <!-- Parties Involved -->
                <p><strong>Freelancer Name:</strong> <i>[freelancer_name]</i></p>
                <p><strong>Company Name:</strong> <i>[business_name]</i></p>
                <p><strong>Project Title:</strong> <i>[project_title]</i></p>
                <p><strong>Project Duration:</strong> <i>[project_duration]</i> months (commencing on <i>[start_date]</i> and ending on <i>[end_date]</i>)</p>
                <p><strong>Work Hours:</strong> Flexible, with deadlines agreed upon by both parties.</p>
                <p><strong>Payment Structure:</strong> Per project ($<i>[project_fee]</i>), payable as follows:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>50% upfront upon signing this contract.</li>
                    <li>50% upon completion and delivery of the project.</li>
                </ul>
            

                <!-- Scope of Work -->
                <h6 class="mt-3"><strong>Scope of Work:</strong></h6>
                <p>The freelancer agrees to complete the following tasks as part of this agreement:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><i>[Task 1]</i></li>
                    <li><i>[Task 2]</i></li>
                    <li><i>[Task 3]</i></li>
                </ul>
                <p>Any additional tasks outside the agreed scope will require a separate agreement and additional compensation.</p>
             
                <!-- Deliverables -->
                <h6 class="mt-3"><strong>Deliverables:</strong></h6>
                <p>The freelancer agrees to deliver the following:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><i>[Deliverable 1]</i> by <i>[deadline_1]</i></li>
                    <li><i>[Deliverable 2]</i> by <i>[deadline_2]</i></li>
                    <li><i>[Final Deliverable]</i> by <i>[final_deadline]</i></li>
                </ul>
               

                <!-- Payment Terms -->
                <h6 class="mt-3"><strong>Payment Terms:</strong></h6>
                <p>Payment will be made as follows:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Payment Method: <i>[payment_method]</i> (e.g., bank transfer, PayPal, etc.).</li>
                    <li>Late Payment: A late fee of 5% will be applied for payments not made within 7 days of the due date.</li>
                </ul>
            

                <!-- Revisions and Edits -->
                <h6 class="mt-3"><strong>Revisions and Edits:</strong></h6>
                <p>The freelancer agrees to provide up to <i>[number_of_revisions]</i> revisions at no additional cost. Any further revisions will be billed at $<i>[revision_rate]</i> per hour.</p>
               

                <!-- Confidentiality Clause -->
                <h6 class="mt-3"><strong>Confidentiality:</strong></h6>
                <p>The freelancer agrees not to disclose any confidential information about the client, their business, or the project during or after the term of this agreement. This includes, but is not limited to, trade secrets, business strategies, and client data.</p>
              

                <!-- Ownership of Work -->
                <h6 class="mt-3"><strong>Ownership of Work:</strong></h6>
                <p>Upon full payment, all rights, title, and interest in the deliverables, including intellectual property rights, will transfer to the client. The freelancer retains the right to display the work in their portfolio unless otherwise agreed in writing.</p>
                

                <!-- Termination Clause -->
                <h6 class="mt-3"><strong>Termination:</strong></h6>
                <p>This contract may be terminated under the following conditions:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>By the client, with 14 days' written notice and payment for work completed up to the termination date.</li>
                    <li>By the freelancer, with 14 days' written notice.</li>
                    <li>Immediately, in cases of breach of contract by either party.</li>
                </ul>
               

                <!-- Dispute Resolution -->
                <h6 class="mt-3"><strong>Dispute Resolution:</strong></h6>
                <p>Any disputes arising from this contract shall be resolved through mediation or arbitration in accordance with the laws of <i>[state/country]</i>.</p>
               

                <!-- Governing Law -->
                <h6 class="mt-3"><strong>Governing Law:</strong></h6>
                <p>This contract shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of <i>[state/country]</i>.</p>
             

                <!-- Signatures -->
                <p class="text-muted">This contract is legally binding.</p>
                <p>Signed by: __________________ (Client) &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Date: <i>[signature_date]</i></p>
                <p>Signed by: __________________ (Freelancer) &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Date: <i>[freelancer_sign_date]</i></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>